metadata.name: Road to power, 'three-legged crow' part 1
metadata.description:
"Ugh... this is... where..." 
When he woke up, he found himself naked. 
As he stood up slowly, a huge 'three-legged crow' pattern appeared in front of him. 
And some voice came. 
"You want power. Come this way." 
He started walking towards the red-lighted hallway.
